OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776197153
OL,3,CHow Trump's Strait of Hormuz blockade
OL,4,Cis pulling China off the sidelines
OL,6,FOn the face of it, China has only
OL,7,Fplayed a minor mediatory role in the
OL,8,FUS-Iran war, meeting with Pakistani
OL,9,Fofficials and apparently helping to
OL,10,Fconvince the Iranians to join peace
OL,11,Ftalks in Islamabad.
OL,13,FBut Beijing has a huge economic stake
OL,14,Fin this war and that is what has
OL,15,Fprompted the sternest warning so far
OL,16,Ffrom the Chinese Foreign Ministry,
OL,17,Fdescribing US President Donald Trump's
OL,18,Fdecision to blockade the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz as "dangerous and
OL,20,Firresponsible".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
