PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776197153
OL,3,CHow Trump's Strait of Hormuz blockade
OL,4,Cis pulling China off the sidelines
OL,6,FReports over the weekend suggested
OL,7,Fthat a shipment of dual-use
OL,8,Ftechnologies and component parts was
OL,9,Fmaking its way from China to Iran via
OL,10,Fthird countries.
OL,12,FThe foreign ministry in Beijing has
OL,13,Flabelled those reports as "groundless
OL,14,Fsmears" and an attempt to "hype"
OL,15,FChina's role in the Iran war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776197153
OL,3,CHow Trump's Strait of Hormuz blockade
OL,4,Cis pulling China off the sidelines
OL,6,FIt is almost impossible to confirm
OL,7,Fsuch a shipment is taking place, but
OL,8,Fwe do know that China provides an
OL,9,Feconomic lifeline for Iran, buying
OL,10,Fsanctioned oil and selling dual-use
OL,11,Ftechnology.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThere is also evidence that some of
OL,19,Fthe weapons used by Iran in this war
OL,20,Fhave come in part or whole from China.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776197153
OL,3,CHow Trump's Strait of Hormuz blockade
OL,4,Cis pulling China off the sidelines
OL,6,FFor years the Chinese have supplied
OL,7,FIran with drones, missiles, component
OL,8,Fparts and even chemicals that support
OL,9,Fthe country's military capabilities.
OL,11,FIt's also believed that together with
OL,12,Fthe Russians, the Chinese have
OL,13,Fprovided satellite intelligence to the
OL,14,FIranians.
OL,16,FDonald Trump has already postponed his
OL,17,Fmuch-heralded state visit to China
OL,18,Fonce, but it's currently scheduled to
OL,19,Ftake place in mid-May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
